graph TD
    db[(Source Database)] -->|WAL Changes| connector[Debezium Connector]
    
    subgraph PyDebeziumAI Library Ingestion
        connector -->|Connect Mode: JPype| jvm_direct[SourceRecordExtractor<br/>JVM Direct Memory]
        connector -->|JSON Mode| json_broker[ConnectMessageExtractor<br/>JSON Parser]
    end
    
    jvm_direct --> canonical[Canonical Model Layer<br/>DebeziumEventModel]
    json_broker --> canonical
    
    subgraph PyDebeziumAI Core Pipeline
        canonical --> transform[Transformation Layer<br/>DocumentBuilder / Sanitizer]
        transform --> sync[Synchronization Layer<br/>SyncManager / Retry / DLQ]
    end
    
    subgraph Vector Store Adapters
        sync --> chroma[Chroma Adapter]
        sync --> pgvector[PGVector Adapter]
        sync --> milvus[Milvus Adapter]
    end
